  "texts": [
    "• ReClor (Yu et al, 2020b).",
    "The ReClor dataset originates from standardized graduate entrance examinations, aiming to heighten the complexity of reading comprehension and introduce novel challenges to the logical reasoning capabilities of models.",
    "In order to mitigate the risk of models achieving elevated performance without a true comprehension of the text through the exploitation of inherent biases in the data, the dataset bias has been partitioned by the creators into easy and hard subsets.",
    "(2) Cloze Test",
    "• ChID (Zheng et al, 2019)."
  ]
}